import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='Penicillin', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['Penicillin'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Mean')
    plt.axvline(data['Penicillin'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Median')
    plt.legend()
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.xlabel('Penicillin Effectiveness')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of Penicillin effectiveness against the bacteria?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.set(style="whitegrid")
    ax = sns.boxplot(x="variable", y="value", data=pd.melt(data[['Streptomycin', 'Neomycin']]))
    ax.set(xlabel='', ylabel='Effectiveness')
    ax.set_xticklabels(['Streptomycin', 'Neomycin'])
    plt.title('How does the effectiveness of Streptomycin compare to that of Neomycin?', wrap=True)
    plt.axhline(y=data['Streptomycin'].median(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Streptomycin Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['Streptomycin'].median()))
    plt.axhline(y=data['Neomycin'].median(), color='b', linestyle='--', label='Neomycin Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['Neomycin'].median()))
    plt.legend()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

    plt.legend()
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.set(style="whitegrid")
    ax = sns.boxplot(x="Genus", y="Streptomycin", data=data, palette="Set3")
    ax.set(xlabel='Bacteria Genus', ylabel='Effectiveness of Streptomycin')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of effectiveness of Streptomycin against different bacteria genera?', wrap=True)
    plt.axhline(y=data['Streptomycin'].median(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['Streptomycin'].median()))
    plt.legend(loc='best')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
